rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0001
rows.name: This is the place we live.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0002
rows.name:
Until we finish the registration process, you'll be staying here
as our guest for a while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_JNK0010
rows.name: Show Interest

rows.label: xs01040100_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask in detail about registration.

rows.label: xs01040100_JNK0020
rows.name: Complaint

rows.label: xs01040100_SEL0021
rows.name: Shake head, indicating you don't want to register.

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0003
rows.name: I'll talk about that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0004
rows.name: You look dissatisfied.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0005
rows.name: So you're the newly recovered crew member?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0005_m
rows.name: So you're the newly recovered crew member?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0005_f
rows.name: So you're the newly recovered crew member?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0006
rows.name: Uncle Nagi![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0007
rows.name: Lin-kun, lively as ever, I see.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0008
rows.name: Yep! Being lively is my trademark![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0009
rows.name:
Speaking of which, on the way here,
I met an unusually grumpy Doug[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0010
rows.name: Did something happen during the test flight?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0011
rows.name: [ST:wide ]―N-nothing happened.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0012
rows.name: I see. Well, that's fine then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0013
rows.name:
More importantly, Elma, good work.
You did well bringing another one here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0014
rows.name: I just carried out my mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0015
rows.name: Now then, about your registration process[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0016
rows.name: Let's continue this inside.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0017
rows.name: There's a lot you need to know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0018
rows.name: My apologies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0019
rows.name:
You've only just woken up, and
Elma must be tired from her mission too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0020
rows.name: Yes, let's do that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs01040100_MSG0021
rows.name: I'll make some tea.[ST:wait ]
